Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:10.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H3B3D4F&\fs12\frz349.9\pos(317.714,162.856)}2年C班  姓名  鸢泽美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:10.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H3B3D4F&\fs12\frz350.1\pos(275.857,190.286)}退部理由  个人原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有笔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1\shad0\bord0\c&H304546&\fs18\pos(314.286,62.286)\frz358.2}退部申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体_GBK\b1\shad0\bord0\c&H304546&\fs32\frz358.2\pos(282.285,65.713)}×
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H3F494C&\fs12\pos(269.143,98.285)\frz356.9}我希望退出社团  飞翔竞技部。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H4D5153&\fs12\pos(301.143,150.856)\frz355.6}2年C班  姓名  鸢泽美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华文中宋\shad0\bord0\c&H333738&\fs12\frz355.1\pos(236.429,186.857)}退部理由  个人原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不是回来  是重新加入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:23.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说  你是新部员喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:26.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:28.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,从今天开始请叫我真白前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:29.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}无敌的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:38.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}追逐星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:44.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}答案一定在天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:50.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}无限的世界冲破黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:58.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}响彻天际的意志  就是天空霸者Zephilion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个就是Zehilion？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:40.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,学姐  说错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样可算不上ZePhilion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,明日香头上的翅膀原来是JePhilion的翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是错了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:51.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是小的时候  岛上的一个孩子给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,岛上的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,像是女版的教练…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:58.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:00.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,小时候的事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:05.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,说起来也有点像我以前挑战过的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,不会是同一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:11.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:48.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的FC很华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:50.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,6点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:51.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,教练
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.11,0:23:54.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这也是为了FC吗？
